    "First, we use the post-Manne treatment indicator as the label to be predicted.",
    "All of the lasso-selected variables are kept.",
    "Second, we run separate lasso regressions with these interaction features as inputs and the conservatism measures as outcomes.",
    "For each outcome, we add the additional covariates selected from the outcome lassos.",
    "This table shows the number of year-covariate terms selected by the double lasso process, by outcome."
